{"tid":146024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【萬事皆可能】唐氏女想做天氣女郎 18萬人支持 電視台爭住請佢","createTime":"2017-03-06T16:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T12:32:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":40,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b80fb4ebe05f87f896f5c3c5f0e4324f5769d39","tid":146024,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170306/56391111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170306%2F56391111&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y95ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=5aecb2e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170306%2F56391111&h=58ec3323\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170306/56391111</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170306/large/1488787131_aa47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170306%2Flarge%2F1488787131_aa47.jpg&h=4554fd02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170306/large/1488787133_2c9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170306%2Flarge%2F1488787133_2c9f.jpg&h=a862375e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敢於突破自我，往往有意想不到的驚喜。法國一名21歲患有唐氏綜合症（Down syndrome）的女子一直希望成為天氣女郎，在慈善團體協助下隨即有電視台伸手邀約，令她即將夢想成真。<br />\n<br />\n慈善團體Unapei為西格（M&eacute;lanie S&eacute;gard）設立facebook專頁，說出她的夢想，又下戰書如果專頁有10萬個「讚好」，就請求法國傳媒邀請西格做天氣女郎。想不到網民反應熱烈，幾天之內已達到18萬個「讚好」，令人喜出望外。<br />\n擁有甜美笑容的西格說︰「我是與眾不同，但我想讓大家知道，我也懂得做很多事，我希望在電視亮相來證明這一點。」國營電視台France 2和BFMTV都相繼邀請她做天氣女郎，她會在本月27日處女登場為大家報道天氣呢。<br />\n英國《都巿報》"},{"pid":"61bfba8cee0cc6c81bcbc2e716a26b01db3e6efb","tid":146024,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17317da900e3d59231bd19382389f77eecef2e81","tid":146024,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cbbfc93905ca2a37089501bb319045e803da0f","tid":146024,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080b83c36bb5c3ea10493eb47ef7633b2c946fe8","tid":146024,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:22:03.000Z","msg":"逆向歧視正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab9ec9b837ebe972b395c239569d2d53051b3ee","tid":146024,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>逆向歧視正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n左膠掌控交明社會"},{"pid":"8e9ea9057e81db8e0e48b1383267ff419ae0a41a","tid":146024,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:23:08.000Z","msg":"成班大愛撚um撚住個良心扮晒支持咁<br />\n咪又係怕群眾壓力"},{"pid":"f048719c1753b0b250150dc636443200f09f5060","tid":146024,"uid":52651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:24:32.000Z","msg":"加油!下次選總統!"},{"pid":"7158bd0e39b45a551b4a358ff2f5395a181e1e52","tid":146024,"uid":11914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:37:22.000Z","msg":"咁點解正常人就要面試， 要篩選？ 係咪歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9eca0602c3cf3f9215ad5c54505a1db441134d","tid":146024,"uid":63,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:38:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點解正常人就要面試， 要篩選？ 係咪歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\